<h1>Installation</h1>
<p class="lead">Get your first Soli MVC application running in under a minute.</p>

<h2>Prerequisites</h2>
<p>Ensure you have the Solilang compiler installed on your system.</p>

<h2>Creating a New Project</h2>
<p>Run the following command to generate a new project:</p>

<div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4 border border-gray-700 my-4 font-mono text-sm">
    <span class="text-green-400">$</span> soli new my_app --mvc
</div>

<h2>Running the Server</h2>
<p>Navigate to your project directory and start the development server:</p>

<div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4 border border-gray-700 my-4 font-mono text-sm">
    <span class="text-green-400">$</span> cd my_app<br>
    <span class="text-green-400">$</span> ./dev.sh
</div>

<p>Your application will be available at <code>http://localhost:3000</code>.</p>
